    dc:date "2023-04-17"^^xsd:date ;
    skos:prefLabel "Qualifications Who We're Looking For • Bachelor degree or above, major in computer, mathematics, statistics • At least 3 years of data product planning and experience design experience, with merchant data product design experience and other data product design experience is preferred • Have great interest in e-commerce and big data industries, have data analysis and mining skills and keen data insight • Proficient in using Axure/Xmind and other design tools, familiar with product flow chart drawing, product requirement document (PRD) and technical function description document writing • Proficient in SQL language, able to find problems and solve problems through data from the data platform • Have certain project management experience, strong execution, and be able to efficiently promote product improvement and project launch • Have excellent team cooperation ability and communication and coordination ability" ;
    pkg:sourceMap "new product Development Professional.mm" .

