pkgc:ID_664167835 a skos:Concept ;
    dc:date "2022-11-23"^^xsd:date ;
    skos:prefLabel "Director, Technical Product Management 1. You will be the Product leader with the highest level of technical expertise in the team. While you will have a team of Product Managers, you are expected to be hands-on and truly be part of the delivery process. Are you comfortable with being more tactical than strategic? 2. Are you willing to create technical user stories/epics to build from scratch a public (client facing) API which will allow clients to accept payments such as credit/debit card, wallets (google pay, PayPal), ACH and instant payment methods? 3. Can you create requirements for Dev teams to build from scratch cross border and local settlement engines? 4. Have you implemented tokenization and fraud monitoring solutions? Product Manager – Data & Analytics 1. Are you comfortable with creating technical user stories for Dev teams to build a multi-country Data/Reporting API with data elements from credit/debit card, ACH, Instant payment, ACH and wallets from scratch? 2. Can you put together a Reconciliation workflow from scratch with specific data elements required for clients to reconcile their daily transactions? 3. Have you previously worked with the following transaction types: authorization, sale, capture, refund, void/reversal? If so, can you build a client facing reporting solution using such transaction types? 4. Are you comfortable with being the Data SME that will ultimately be the owner of the Data strategy for a global Payments platform? Let me know if you have any questions/which one you'd like to go ahead for. I look forward to receiving your resume. Best, Helen" ;
    pkg:hasSubTopic pkgc:ID_672860837 ;
    pkg:sourceMap "new product Development Professional.mm" .

