pkgc:ID_700247241 a skos:Concept ;
    dc:date "2025-11-18"^^xsd:date ;
    skos:prefLabel "1. Business appetite/climate: This tells you how fast you need to show tangible progress or ship. Tony Fadell used to say that if you can’t ship something, or show tangible promise within 6 months, no matter how ambitious that thing is, you’re done. Even if leadership is still on board, your team will lose momentum. Killing your team’s momentum is the worst sin." ;
